cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.IT, cs.GR, cs.NA 

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with image processing and denoising techniques. It may also belong to the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category as digital images are a form of multimedia. Information theory (cs.IT) may also be a relevant sub-category as noise models are related to information theory. Graphics (cs.GR) and numerical analysis (cs.NA) may also be relevant sub-categories as they deal with image processing and noise reduction techniques.
